{
  "stem": "22685.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then I said, I have a friend who was a Pollock from a farmer that I knew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was familiar with horses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had two horses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got the job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there are a lot of things which happened there, but I don't know if they are very important in the things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I worked-- I became important for the organization.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They wanted to put me in charge of a group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Except the Jews-- we had, although, in some places in that state, German girls working-- but German girls not from Germany, but Germans from the German-- it was a German autonomic [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] district in Russia.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was  an autonomic state, Oblast, which was mostly German which had came to Russia during the times of Ivan the Great when they wanted to build, to develop the, the, the country.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they imported German workers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they lived, and they spoke German among themselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when the war broke out, and Russia did it, like, we did here with the Japanese, but not in the same nice way.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They took all the republic through all, all the people from that autonomic-- they called it autonomic republic-- and sent them out to Asia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There they separated-- the men they sent to the coal mines in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is on the Chinese border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The women they sent to the forests to work, the wood forest, in other words.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the old people and the kids remained in Asia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we-- for us, worked a group-- several groups of the German girls.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and I could-- I was without papers ever since I escaped.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But since I worked on a horse-- and nobody has private horses in Russia, nobody.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
